<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink311">
<l>vēṅkai koyyunar pañcuram viḷippiṉu</l>
<l>māriṭaic celvō rāṟunaṉi verūuṅ</l>
<l>kāṭiṟan taṉarē kātalar</l>
<l>nīṭuvar kolleṉa niṉaiyumeṉ ṉeñcē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] beloved traversed the wilderness,</l>
<l>where travelers through dangerous places are much scared on their way,</l>
<l>even when women, plucking Kino tree flowers, </l>
<l>sing pañcuram melody.</l>
<l>“Will he stay there?”, my heart thinks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
